<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Work</title>
    <style>
        /* Embedded CSS for quick styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ecd9c6; /* Light brown background */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #000000; /* Dark brown text color */
        }

        p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6d6d6d; /* Lighter brown text color */
        }

        .work-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .work-item img {
                width: 150px;
                height: auto;
                margin-right: 20px;
                border-radius: 8px; /* Rounded corners for images */
            }

        .work-item-details {
            flex: 2;
        }

        .price {
            color: #00a82d; /* Green for price */
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .description {
            color: #4a4a4a; /* Dark brown for description */
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #4a4a4a;
            color: #fff; /* White text color */
            padding: 10px 0; /* Adjust padding as needed */
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>My Work</h1>
        <p>This is where the 'art' is stored.</p>

        <div class="work-item">
            <img src="/images/pottery.jpg" alt="Pottery Pot">
            <div class="work-item-details">
                <p class="price"><a href="product1" style="color: #00a82d;">Price: R900</a></p>
                <p class="description">This blue pot was handcrafted in southern Africa by tribes of the Anglos.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="work-item">
            <img src="/images/wood.jpg" alt="Wooden Sculpture">
            <div class="work-item-details">
                <p class="price"><a href="product2" style="color: #00a82d;">Price: R1600</a></p>
                <p class="description">This wooden sculpture represents the essence of nature, carved by skilled artisans.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="work-item">
            <img src="/images/furtniture.jpg" alt="Table">
            <div class="work-item-details">
                <p class="price"><a href="product3" style="color: #00a82d;">Price: R3500</a></p>
                <p class="description">This table was hand carved, oiled and perfectly designed by an artisan with a full for useful art.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 My Work. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>